01:48.133 --> 01:50.155
Excuse me.

02:01.483 --> 02:03.772
There's so many people.

02:03.772 --> 02:06.914
All of a sudden, there's so many people.

02:09.054 --> 02:11.593
The market's just closed.

02:12.214 --> 02:15.681
Okay, angel, I have appointments.

02:18.460 --> 02:20.688
