02:20.688 --> 02:23.466
That might be it for a while.

02:25.589 --> 02:28.021
Don't let 'em change you.

02:28.021 --> 02:30.331
Promise me.

02:30.331 --> 02:32.680
Why fix what's not broken?

02:40.140 --> 02:43.140
Mrs. Paulsen said she'd be in early
this morning to pick up her glasses.

02:43.815 --> 02:46.370
