04:38.509 --> 04:41.509
Travel cases, cleaning solution, contact lenses.

04:48.475 --> 04:50.018
Excuse me.

04:50.018 --> 04:52.871
In the mornings, he straightens up out here,

04:52.871 --> 04:54.254
you went in the back?

04:54.254 --> 04:57.254
Every morning for two years.

04:58.084 --> 05:01.084
